{"type": "article", "id": 57528, "title": "《猫和老鼠》要有真人动画电影了，明年开始拍摄", "description": "你的童年记忆是不是又被唤醒了？", "date": "2018-10-20T22:50:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 53450, "name": "猫和老鼠"}, {"id": 53609, "name": "真人动画电影"}, {"id": 2230, "name": "华纳兄弟"}, {"id": 53610, "name": "提姆·史多利"}], "category": 3, "author": 1428461, "comment_count": 35, "praise_count": 87, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181020204608ycMOLiteRWGnKd1w.jpg", "contents": "<p align=\"left\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">近日，<a href=\"https://variety.com/2018/film/news/tom-and-jerry-scooby-doo-tim-story-warner-animation-1202978052/\" rel=\"nofollow\">有消息称</a>美国华纳兄弟将计划拍摄《猫和老鼠》( Tom and Jerry )的真人动画电影。导演是提姆·史多利。他拍摄的电影&nbsp;<i>Shaft&nbsp;</i>将于明年上映。此外，他的代表作有《一路向前》(&nbsp;<i>Ride Along&nbsp;</i>)《男人行不行》(&nbsp;<i>Think Like a Man&nbsp;</i>)《哈拉大发师》(&nbsp;<i>Barbershop&nbsp;</i>)《神奇四侠系列电影》(&nbsp;<i>Fantastic Four&nbsp;</i>)等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181020204907OcFrGeWsuN14yR8p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.009040\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">导演提姆·史多利，图来自 <a href=\"https://www.indiewire.com/2014/01/tim-story-the-top-grossing-black-director-many-apparently-still-arent-familiar-with-162508/\" rel=\"nofollow\">indiewire</a></figcaption></figure></div><p align=\"left\">在这部真人动画版的《猫和老鼠》中，两个主角猫和老鼠将由动画代替，而且有趣的是，他们将保持无声。尽管这些年来已经有很多有关于《猫和老鼠》的电影了，但是<a href=\"http://screencrush.com/tom-and-jerry-live-action-movie/\" rel=\"nofollow\">真人动画版这还是第一部</a>。</p><p align=\"left\">真人动画版的《猫和老鼠》<a href=\"https://variety.com/2018/film/news/tom-and-jerry-scooby-doo-tim-story-warner-animation-1202978052/\" rel=\"nofollow\">将于明年开始拍摄</a>。</p><p class=\"\">\n\n\n\n\n\n</p><p align=\"left\">此外，华纳兄弟的电影工作室还在同时筹备另一部新的动画电影——《史酷比，你在哪里？》，导演是执导过《小鬼当家》《窈窕奶爸》《哈利波特与魔法石》等作品的克里斯·哥伦布。这部电影要等到&nbsp;<a href=\"http://screencrush.com/tom-and-jerry-live-action-movie/\" rel=\"nofollow\">2020 年上半年上映</a>。</p><p align=\"left\" class=\"\"><br></p><p align=\"left\" class=\"\">题图为《猫和老鼠》的动画片，题图和文中图来自&nbsp;<a href=\"https://acceleratetv.com/tom-and-jerry-revived-live-action-adaptation/\" rel=\"nofollow\">acceleratetv</a>&nbsp;和 indiewire</p>"}